name: Ahsoka Tano LoRA
description:
Well, I made it for myself then I saw Ahsoka Lora on Civitai and god it's awful. So I decided to publish my Lora.

I recommend use 0.6-0.8 strength.

I divided Ahsoka on 3 age stages: teen(1-6 season)(≠loli), young(7 season) and adult(rebels). If you have problems with this tags you can use ahsoka_teen, ahsoka_young and ahsoka_adult.

Also this beautiful lora allows you to generate different clothes for this orange woman: mandalorian armor, fulcrum clothes(just clothes of adult Ahsoka), padawan clothes, slave clothes(Zygerrian slave) and tatooine clothes(Tatooine slave. But this outfit works bad). If you have problems with this tags use ahsoka_mandalorian_armor, ahsoka_fulcrum, ahsoka_padawan, ahsoka_slave and ahsoka_tatooine_slave.

And it's a STAR WARS so you can generate different lightsabers. Like "green lightsaber" or "blue lightsaber" or "white lightsaber" or my favorite "red lightsaber" or even "turn-off lightsaber". But as you can see my lightsabers suck. So don't use it. Please.

BTW I used some sith Ahsoka images so you can try to use tags dark_ahsoka and sith, but I don't think you will get something cool.

Can you generate NSFW images to see naked Ahsoka? Yeah, you can. But I will judge you.

Thanks for reading and helping with my mental problems.

Inglish bad sorry for.
